tly requests it.","A full refresh or collection rebuild is required after major state changes; incremental refresh alone is insufficient in those cases.","Output must include discarded paths and uncertainty signals — omitting them violates the agent output boundary contract."]},"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"53d90233-9c18-4a8f-8b67-2db79aeb7401"}
